---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us · Love Your Health Natural Medicine" description="Meet the three naturopathic doctors behind Love Your Health Natural Medicine. Women-owned, LGBTQ+ founded, and rooted in empathy — serving Tempe, AZ and virtual patients across Arizona.">

  <!-- ==================== HERO — OUR STORY ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-cream relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[60rem] h-[60rem] rounded-full bg-[#F5E0D0]/20 blur-[140px] -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 lg:mb-14">
        <p class="scroll-reveal text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sage mb-4">About Us</p>
        <h1 class="scroll-reveal text-[clamp(2.2rem,6vw,4.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.06] tracking-[-0.03em] text-charcoal mb-5">
          Medicine built on <span class="text-sage">empathy,</span> not ego.
        </h1>
        <p class="scroll-reveal text-base md:text-lg text-text-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Three naturopathic doctors who know what it feels like to be dismissed — and built a practice so you never have to feel that way again.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Team photo -->
      <div class="scroll-reveal relative rounded-2xl md:rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-charcoal/12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/doctors/fann-bg.jpg"
          alt="The Love Your Health team — Dr. Bailey, Dr. Carie, and Dr. Spencer in their Tempe, AZ clinic"
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover aspect-[16/9] md:aspect-[2.2/1]"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/40 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 px-6 md:px-10 pb-5 md:pb-7">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-2 shadow-sm">
              <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Est. February 2024 · Tempe, AZ</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== ORIGIN STORY ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] rounded-full bg-sage-pale/30 blur-[120px] -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/4 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">

        <!-- Left: narrative -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal">
          <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-terracotta mb-4">How it started</p>
          <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-6">
            We became doctors because <span class="text-sage">no one listened</span> to us first.
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-text-light leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Before they were doctors, Carie and Spencer were patients — navigating chronic health issues that conventional medicine couldn't explain. The same frustrating cycle: rushed appointments, normal labs, and no real answers.
            </p>
            <p>
              That experience changed everything. They both discovered naturopathic medicine, trained at Sonoran University of Health Sciences, and made a promise: to build the kind of practice they wished they'd had.
            </p>
            <p>
              In February 2024, they opened Love Your Health Natural Medicine in Tempe, AZ — and brought Dr. Bailey Newman on board to complete a team that listens first and treats the whole person, not just the symptoms.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: timeline -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.15s;">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 lg:p-10 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-8">Our Journey</p>

            <div class="space-y-0">
              <!-- Milestone 1 -->
              <div class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-terracotta icon-pulse"></div>
                  <div class="w-0.5 flex-1 bg-sage-pale mt-1"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-8">
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-terracotta mb-1">The Spark</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Both founders dealt with chronic health issues — IBS, hormonal imbalances, and fatigue — and were dismissed by conventional doctors. They knew there had to be a better way.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Milestone 2 -->
              <div class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-sage icon-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
                  <div class="w-0.5 flex-1 bg-sage-pale mt-1"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-8">
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-sage mb-1">Sonoran University</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Both earned their naturopathic medical degrees from Sonoran University of Health Sciences — one of the top naturopathic programs in the country. Dr. Carie also completed a registered dietitian credential.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Milestone 3 -->
              <div class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-terracotta icon-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
                  <div class="w-0.5 flex-1 bg-sage-pale mt-1"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-8">
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-terracotta mb-1">Residency & Training</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Dr. Spencer gained clinical experience at Mayo Clinic. Dr. Carie joined Sonoran's faculty, teaching nutrition, IV therapy, and medical ethics. Dr. Bailey honed her skills in digestive health and acupuncture.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Milestone 4 -->
              <div class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-sage icon-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-sage mb-1">February 2024 — LYHNM Opens</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Love Your Health Natural Medicine opened its doors in Tempe, AZ. Three doctors, one team, and a mission to bring root-cause medicine to everyone who's been told "your labs are normal."</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== MISSION & PHILOSOPHY ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[#F5E0D0] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[50rem] h-[50rem] rounded-full bg-white/15 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 lg:mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-terracotta mb-4">Our philosophy</p>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-5">
          Find the why. Treat the <span class="text-sage">whole person.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-text-light leading-relaxed">
          We don't just manage symptoms — we investigate, listen, and build care plans that address what's actually going on.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3-column pillars -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">

        <!-- Pillar 1: Root-Cause Medicine -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 lg:p-10 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sage icon-search" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-charcoal mb-3">Root-Cause Medicine</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">We don't stop at "what" — we find the "why." Advanced labs, comprehensive health histories, and the detective work most doctors skip. Your symptoms have a source, and we'll find it.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 2: Whole-Person Care -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 lg:p-10 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-terracotta/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-terracotta icon-heartbeat" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-charcoal mb-3">Whole-Person Care</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Your body doesn't work in isolated systems — and neither do we. We look at nutrition, hormones, mental health, lifestyle, and environment together. Because everything is connected.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 3: Patient Empowerment -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 lg:p-10 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-earth/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-earth icon-zap" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-charcoal mb-3">Patient Empowerment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">We don't just hand you a treatment plan — we educate you about your body so you understand why each step matters. You become an active partner in your own healing.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== MEET THE DOCTORS — EXPANDED BIOS ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-cream relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] rounded-full bg-sage-pale/20 blur-[120px] translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 lg:mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-terracotta mb-4">Your care team</p>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-5">
          The doctors behind <span class="text-sage">the mission.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-text-light leading-relaxed">
          Every patient gets the combined expertise of all three doctors — because your health deserves more than one perspective.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Doctor Cards — full-width horizontal -->
      <div class="space-y-8">

        <!-- Dr. Carie Perrino -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-sage-pale/40">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0">
            <div class="lg:col-span-4 relative overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src="/images/doctors/team-photo.jpg"
                alt="Dr. Carie Perrino, NMD, RDN, CLT — Co-Founder of Love Your Health Natural Medicine"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top aspect-[4/3] lg:aspect-auto min-h-[300px]"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
                <span class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-terracotta text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Co-Founder</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-8 p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-charcoal mb-1">Dr. Carie Perrino</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-sage font-semibold mb-4">NMD, RDN, CLT · Co-Founder</p>
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-5">
                Dr. Carie's own battle with IBS and chronic digestive issues led her to naturopathic medicine. A registered dietitian turned naturopathic doctor, she brings a rare dual expertise to every patient. She's now faculty at Sonoran University, teaching nutrition, IV therapy, and medical ethics to the next generation of naturopathic doctors.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-5 text-sm">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-light/50 mb-1">Education</p>
                  <p class="text-charcoal font-medium">BS Nutritional Sciences, Mizzou · Sonoran University</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-light/50 mb-1">Specialties</p>
                  <p class="text-charcoal font-medium">Gut Health · Mold Illness · Hormones · Nutrition</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                <span class="bg-sage-pale text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Faculty at Sonoran University</span>
                <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Registered Dietitian</span>
                <a href="/doctors/dr-perrino" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-sage hover:text-sage-dark transition-colors ml-auto">
                  Full bio
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr. Spencer Warren -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-sage-pale/40" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0">
            <div class="lg:col-span-4 relative overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src="/images/doctors/spencer-headshot.jpg"
                alt="Dr. Spencer Warren, NMD — Co-Founder of Love Your Health Natural Medicine"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top aspect-[4/3] lg:aspect-auto min-h-[300px]"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
                <span class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-sage text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Co-Founder</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-8 p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-charcoal mb-1">Dr. Spencer Warren</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-sage font-semibold mb-4">NMD · Co-Founder</p>
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-5">
                Dr. Spencer graduated magna cum laude from ASU with a BS in Nutrition & Dietetics before earning her naturopathic medical degree from Sonoran University. Her prior clinical work at Mayo Clinic gives her a unique perspective that bridges conventional and naturopathic medicine. She's passionate about fertility, GI health, and cardiovascular wellness.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-5 text-sm">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-light/50 mb-1">Education</p>
                  <p class="text-charcoal font-medium">BS Nutrition & Dietetics, ASU (magna cum laude) · Sonoran University</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-light/50 mb-1">Specialties</p>
                  <p class="text-charcoal font-medium">Fertility · GI Health · Cardiovascular · Hormones</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                <span class="bg-sage-pale text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Mayo Clinic Experience</span>
                <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Magna Cum Laude</span>
                <a href="/doctors/dr-warren" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-sage hover:text-sage-dark transition-colors ml-auto">
                  Full bio
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr. Bailey Newman -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-sage-pale/40" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0">
            <div class="lg:col-span-4 relative overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src="/images/doctors/bailey-headshot.jpeg"
                alt="Dr. Bailey Newman, NMD — Naturopathic Doctor at Love Your Health Natural Medicine"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top aspect-[4/3] lg:aspect-auto min-h-[300px]"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
                <span class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-earth text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Naturopathic Doctor</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-8 p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-charcoal mb-1">Dr. Bailey Newman</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-sage font-semibold mb-4">NMD</p>
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-5">
                Dr. Bailey brings a unique blend of scientific rigor and cultural awareness to her practice. With dual degrees in Physiology and Spanish Literature from the University of Arizona, she's fluent in both English and Spanish — making care more accessible to the community. She specializes in digestive health, women's health, and acupuncture.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-5 text-sm">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-light/50 mb-1">Education</p>
                  <p class="text-charcoal font-medium">BA Physiology + Spanish Literature, U of A · Sonoran University</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-light/50 mb-1">Specialties</p>
                  <p class="text-charcoal font-medium">Digestive Health · Women's Health · Acupuncture</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                <span class="bg-sage-pale text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Bilingual (EN/ES)</span>
                <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Acupuncture</span>
                <a href="/doctors/dr-newman" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-sage hover:text-sage-dark transition-colors ml-auto">
                  Full bio
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] rounded-full bg-[#F5E0D0]/20 blur-[120px] translate-x-1/4 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-10 lg:mb-14 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sage mb-4">What makes us different</p>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal">
          Not your typical <span class="text-sage">doctor's office.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Bento Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-12 auto-rows-[minmax(140px,auto)] gap-4 lg:gap-5">

        <!-- Women-Owned (tall left) -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt col-span-4 md:col-span-5 md:row-span-2 bg-sage rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 lg:p-10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-full border border-white/10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-28 h-28 rounded-full border border-white/10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our practice</p>
              <p class="text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-black text-white leading-[1] tracking-tight mb-2">Women-<br/>Owned</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-bold text-white/80">& Operated</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed mt-6 max-w-xs">All three of our doctors are women who built this practice from scratch — because they knew healthcare could be better.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- LGBTQ+ Founded -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt col-span-4 md:col-span-7 bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 lg:p-10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300" style="transition-delay: 0.06s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#F5E0D0] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-terracotta icon-heartbeat" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-terracotta mb-2">LGBTQ+ Founded & Friendly</p>
              <p class="font-bold text-charcoal text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-snug mb-2">A safe space for <span class="text-sage">everyone.</span></p>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Our practice was founded by members of the LGBTQ+ community. Inclusivity isn't an afterthought — it's in our DNA.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
